title: The Clues! | American Horror Story Season 10 Double Feature | It's the 70's? #AHS
author: GrayArea
comment: I’m calling it. They are definitely involving Sirens this season. I feel like the clues are there. Especially with the sea aspect
we want aliens because of the end of Asylum. We are waiting for aliens to tie into the end of season 2.
I think the real reason people are wanting aliens is because of who they have with them. If the same ones from Asylum come back, there's a chance we might get to see Kit Walker again.
Satanic panic was big in 1970s too. That could be why the 70s is the story by the sand if we continue with the witch idea. What fun!
description:
American Horror Story Season 10 Double Feature Clues have been coming out and I have gathered all of the clues and decided to sleuth over them! In this video I will show you why I think AHS Season 10 Double Feature is about Urban Legends and atleast one of these stories is set in 1970! Thanks for Watching!
